And actually, I heard during a conference
that squared edges on buttons actually

22
00:01:00.620 --> 00:01:03.900
draw the user's attention more than
rounded border radius buttons like round

23
00:01:03.900 --> 00:01:07.210
buttons because there's more pixels for
the user's eye to be drawn to.

24
00:01:07.210 --> 00:01:09.260
So that's just an interesting, fun fact.

25
00:01:09.260 --> 00:01:11.920
But ghost buttons yeah, you would
typically see for a secondary button.

26
00:01:13.980 --> 00:01:15.162
We have icon buttons,

27
00:01:15.162 --> 00:01:18.660
so there are ones without labels
