assistive technology does not
know what this is going to do.

30
00:01:24.200 --> 00:01:26.240
If you can use a label,
use a label please.

31
00:01:27.730 --> 00:01:30.687
We'll talk about that when
we actually code these.

32
00:01:32.475 --> 00:01:34.270
So button styles.

33
00:01:34.270 --> 00:01:36.628
So border radius,
we all know border radius probably.

34
00:01:36.628 --> 00:01:41.573
These are gonna be a little bit more
playful than a traditional 90 degree

35
00:01:41.573 --> 00:01:44.060
perpendicular button edge.

36
00:01:44.060 --> 00:01:47.030
But think back to your brand identity,
think back to your design principles.

37
00:01:47.030 --> 00:01:51.340
If you wanna be bold and energetic,
maybe border radius is fun to incorporate.

38
00:01:51.340 --> 00:01:53.960
If you're building something
that's very professional,

39
00:01:53.960 --> 00:01:55.820
you might want to stick with square edges.

40
00:01:58.100 --> 00:01:59.920
Drop shadow is also cool.

