It plays very nicely and so you can
see here we've got multiples of 4 for

68
00:03:29.650 --> 00:03:30.827
our top and bottom padding.

69
00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.092
And horizontal padding,

70
00:03:34.092 --> 00:03:36.621
you can add a horizontal padding
