it's not gonna be responsive but

72
00:03:39.428 --> 00:03:42.250
if you set padding,
it's gonna be a little bit nicer.

73
00:03:42.250 --> 00:03:43.140
It's gonna play a little nicer.

74
00:03:43.140 --> 00:03:45.050
You can set minimum
widths on these as well.

75
00:03:45.050 --> 00:03:49.780
So if you have just an icon button,
you can make it min width 100 pixels, so

76
00:03:49.780 --> 00:03:52.170
it's not gonna be super tiny,
still accessible.

